up plans to expand nursery education.
She announced that she had set up a special taskforce in her department to
implement the promise to increase nursery provision made by Mr John Major,
the prime minister, at last month's Cons-ervative party conference.
Mrs Shephard said the commitment was to provide, over time, good quality
