                                      average tariff (%)
Country or group                Pre-       Post-       Average
                             Uruguay     Uruguay       tariff
                              Round       Round        cut (%)
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
Developed countries            6.3         3.9            38
Canada                         9.0         4.8            47
European Union                 5.7         3.6            37
Japan                          3.9         1.7            56
