FT  01 NOV 94 / World News in Brief: Up to 68 dead in US air crash
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
An American Eagle commuter aircraft carrying 64 passengers and four crew
from Indianapolis crashed while attempting to land at Chicago's O'Hare
airport. There were reported to be no survivors.
