                             CLIMATE
 -------------------------------------------------------------------
The regional climate varies from mild winters with temperatures
ranging from zero to 15 degrees Centigrade, to hot and steamy
summers with temperatures ranging from 17 to 31 degrees.
Fortunately, spring and autumn are long and pleasant.
