</XX>
<IN>P794  Commercial Sports.
    P8699 Membership Organizations, NEC.
</IN>
<XX>
Types:-
</XX>
<TP>PEOP  People.
    CMMT  Comment &amp; Analysis.
</TP>
<XX>
People:-
</XX>
<PE>Payne, B Atlanta Committee for the Olympic Games.
</PE>
