 --------------------------------------------------------------
Company            Sales   Change on    Recurring   Change on
                            year (%)    profits**    year (%)
 --------------------------------------------------------------
Nippon Paper       316.2     -0.7          5.6        +39.8
New Oji Paper      270.3    +25.1          6.6        +31.6
Honshu Paper       182.2     -2.0          3.2        -11.2
Daishowa Paper     141.3     -2.4         -6.9            -
