<TEXT>
Andayani Megah, an Indonesian tyre cord manufacturer which is part of the
Gajah Tunggal Group, and a unit of Malaysia's Hicom Holdings Berhad are
setting up a joint venture to build Malaysia's first tyre cord manufacturing
plant, writes Manuela Saragosa in Jakarta.
