rule that requires more than 25 per cent of the share capital to be in
public hands.
Tasman Agriculture, VDL's majority shareholder, is to make the minority
shareholders a cash offer for their shares following the delisting. The
directors of VDL will then announce details of a rights issue to finance
development of the Woolnorth farming assets.
